  "3336430": {
    "name": "MeMic",
    "steam_appid": 3336430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/b0b8787afa115fda4734866e64650d11.poster.avif?t=1741719301\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/b0b8787afa115fda4734866e64650d11.webm?t=1741719301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/b0b8787afa115fda4734866e64650d11.mp4?t=1741719301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MeMic</strong> 是一款充满氛围的潜行游戏，融合了恐怖元素。在游戏中，你将扮演一个可以伪装成日常物品的拟态怪。沉浸在一个黑暗的世界中，每个物品都成为生存的工具，而敌人的每一步都可能是你最后的步伐。你的目标不仅是躲避危险，还要探索一个充满彩蛋和致敬热门游戏及流行文化的世界，为每位玩家带来独特体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/3f75735f326d6da104f7a7e7f5fdcb87.poster.avif?t=1741719301\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/3f75735f326d6da104f7a7e7f5fdcb87.webm?t=1741719301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/3f75735f326d6da104f7a7e7f5fdcb87.mp4?t=1741719301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>伪装玩法:</strong> 利用你的拟态能力，变身为附近的任意物品——从宝箱到家具。躲避敌人，观察他们的巡逻路线，并选择最佳时机发动攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>狩猎与生存:</strong> 参与一场危险的生存游戏。保持不被发现需要精心策划，因为每个动作和攻击都必须精确时机。你能否躲避冒险者的追击并最终获胜？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>氛围场景:</strong> 每个关卡都经过精心打造，从照明到环境动画无不细致入微。这些沉浸式场景将你带入一个紧张感不断升级的世界，即使是最微小的细节也可能决定你的命运。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/7bc8f783dd3825acc51655e7c9bc2152.poster.avif?t=1741719301\" width=600 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/7bc8f783dd3825acc51655e7c9bc2152.webm?t=1741719301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336430/extras/7bc8f783dd3825acc51655e7c9bc2152.mp4?t=1741719301\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>秘密和彩蛋:</strong> MeMic 充满了对其他游戏、标志性宇宙以及幽默细节的隐秘致敬。每个关卡都隐藏着小秘密，让玩家在探索中感受到自己仿佛成为了游戏文化的一部分。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>技能评分:</strong> 每个关卡结束后，你将根据完成目标的速度和安全程度获得从 S 到 D 的评分。不断挑战关卡，优化策略，提升技能！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>准备迎接挑战了吗？</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入一个每个角落都隐藏着谜团、每个物品都可能成为你的庇护所的世界。MeMic 将扣人心弦的潜行玩法、幽默和浓厚氛围完美融合。准备好探索、伪装、生存了吗——你能揭开这个世界所有的秘密吗？</p>",
